{"tid":2118654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍與盟友本周在亞洲水域舉行兩次軍事演習","createTime":"2020-07-21T14:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T15:09:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f20b9b0b98bb3c467fdda3986e2bec970bcf1fb","tid":2118654,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:52:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539110-20200721.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539110-20200721.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rjy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=a970e845\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539110-20200721.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fb91b9f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539110-20200721.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國海軍表示，本星期分別與盟友印度、日本及澳洲，在亞洲水域舉行兩次軍事演習。<br />\n<br />\n美軍表示，尼米茲號航空母艦星期一在印度洋，與印度海軍派出的軍艦，舉行的聯合演習，目的是提升兩軍的互通性，包括防空能力。另外，亦派遣列根號航空母艦打擊群到菲律賓海，與日本及澳洲海軍舉行聯合演習，演習將於星期四結束。<br />\n<br />\n軍演正值中美因新型肺炎疫情及香港等問題關係惡化，美國早前亦指控中國聲稱擁有南海島嶼主權的說法是非法。<br />\n<br />\n中國對美國在區內舉行軍演表示反對，又批評美方拒絕承認中方擁有南海島嶼的主權，加劇地區緊張局勢、破壞地區穩定。"},{"pid":"195ace8da846020d96760c3675e9da2a28b2f86d","tid":2118654,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如直接係南海軍演啦"},{"pid":"83dcf5657b1a4bfd9a27c37a30d813faf457a01e","tid":2118654,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"打喇唔好演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31b64dba171646c8e953afd1360e6d4ec64c9f7","tid":2118654,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:09:39.000Z","msg":"係咪要幫堆東南亞升下level <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}